        {
            "title": "萬科第一季度持續錄得虧損 受結算面積下降拖累",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Company filings\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"635\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5hzFuyApR13x8Noa8C9dTg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/67a3d901ce664876d65e03237d79c505\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Company filings</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 由於房屋交付量下降拖累了萬科企業的整體收入，這家陷入困境的開發商第一季度持續錄得虧損。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據該公司周三向港交所提交的文件，截至3月份的三個月內，萬科淨虧損59.5億元人民幣。這一數字略低於上年同期虧損62.5億元人民幣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萬科過去兩個財年的累計虧損超過1300億元人民幣，這表明在中國房價長期低迷的背景下，盈利持續受到侵蝕。儘管今年第一季度中國新建住宅價格的下跌速度放緩，但在萬科項目集中佈局的多數區域中心城市及中小城市，房價仍在下滑。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-34581252-e1bf-38d9-b92c-fa7c0327550c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家管理資產規模超過1萬億元人民幣的開發商，是目前中國少數尚未發生違約的大型房企之一。但該公司兩年多來一直面臨流動性緊張的局面，近幾個月來更是通過持續的債券展期來爭取更多時間。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">點擊此處查看財報詳情</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"635\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ozOuV8KXD5qMMpo61tWrGA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4e44892df0d557c0fca147854511094b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萬科在財報中表示，虧損主要源於房屋結算的下降。結算面積同比下降33%，導致總收入下降24%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Builder China Vanke Posts $871 Million Loss in First Quarter (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
